casebody.data:
MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

99-1642. Waterloo Coal Co. v. Vinton Cty. Bd. of Revision.

Board of Tax Appeals, No. 97-N-1531. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Board of Tax Appeals. Upon consideration of appellants’ application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
